	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi literas tuas, compater et frater charissime, diligenter de rebus omnibus stris scriptas ac gratias pro iis ago maximas.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Perge sic, ut coepisti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cunctatur rex, quia haeret.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia nunc celebrantur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21" cert="high">Badae</placeName>, necdum militem regi concesserunt nisi <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l160" cert="high">Friburgenses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Salodorii</placeName>; reliqui hactenus nihil concesserunt.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Suspicantur tamen multi regem, ubi liberius numeraverit, militem habiturum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim tamen certum est <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basilienses</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffhusianos</placeName> et illos magis cogitare de renuntiando foedere.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Militem, quem nunc postulat, rex in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName> ducere cogitat, ut liberet et educat exercitum <placeName type="citizen_name">Guysianum</placeName>, cum quo mox per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemontem</placeName> descendat in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgicam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetii</placeName> difficulter concedent militem, qui proficiscatur prius in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italiam</placeName>; vident enim profectionem illam fore periculosissimam.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Also söllend belonet werden, die der heylikeit dienend.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam sapiant aliquando <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rheti</placeName>, ne caesis militibus in servitio aut militia regis tandem cogantur se permittere diripiendos et laniandos <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italis</placeName> atque <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanis</placeName> totam ditionem suam relinquere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1887" cert="high">Athesinis</placeName> et lanzknächtis etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> scribunt amici <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandum</persName> postulasse a <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916">Schertlio</persName> exercitum 5000 peditum et 300 levis armaturae equitum, Schertlium hic omnem suam operam contulisse regi et exquisitum parasse regi exercitum, quem ducat contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2721" cert="high">Pannoniam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ecce, dum expectat, quando vocatur, adest nuncius, qui ostendit regi nihil nunc opus esse exercitu contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName>; proinde milites, quos paravit, mittat <placeName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="l1299">Riedlingam</placeName>, ubi <persName type="auto_name">Pollvylerus</persName> conscripturus sit brevi exercitum 7000 peditum et 1000 equitum, quem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgas</placeName> contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallum</placeName> ducat, nulla interim mentione facta sumptuum etc.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Unde tantum non insaniunt contra <persName ref="p18477" cert="high">Ferdinandum</persName> et capitanei et milites.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Mitt sömlichen fuulen sachen gadt man um.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicitur autem <persName type="citizen_name">Philippus</persName> parasse 3 ordines, primum educet <persName type="citizen_name">dux Sabaudiae</persName> contra <placeName type="citizen_name">Marieburgum</placeName>, secundum <persName type="citizen_name">Gonzaga</persName> (opinor) ducet contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l631" cert="high">Burgundiam</placeName>, in tertio erit ipse <persName type="citizen_name">Philippus</persName> cum suis Inferioris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germaniae</placeName> populis et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglis</placeName>; horum (ut ex Antverpia pridie audivimus) 7000 applicarunt in Inferiore <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germania</placeName> militaturi Philippo contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallum</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summus <persName type="auto_name">imperator Anglorum</persName> est comes <placeName type="auto_name">Penbrüggensis</placeName>, locum tenens d. <persName type="auto_name">Bron</persName>, consiliarii comes <placeName type="auto_name">Ruttlandiae</placeName>, comes <placeName type="auto_name">Bettfordiae</placeName>, d.  <persName type="auto_name">Bray</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Clinchton</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Dudlei</persName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aiunt <persName type="auto_name">Philippum</persName> recta profecturum versus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic scribitur ab <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> quoque et concorditer ex aliis locis; quamquam vero illa non existimem vana esse prorsus, superare tamen rem arbitror famam.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de">Der könig in <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l2464">Franckrych</placeName> wirt denocht nitt also umbzuͦkeren sin,</foreign> nisi forte dies eius iam quoque adsit et vindicta dei incubuerit super eum.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Colloquium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l569" cert="high">Wormacię</placeName> dicitur procedere, sed sine principibus, de quo alias plura, ubi certiora habuero.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="manual" ana="salute">Has literas communes habebis ut et proximas ante 8 dies scriptas cum dd. consulibus, <persName type="auto_name">Philippo</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6831">Traverso</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8432" cert="high">Friderycho a Salyce</persName>, ad quem tuis inclusas mittes omnesque salutabis diligentissime.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Omnes mei te et tuam domum salutant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sis fidelis et diligens in negotio domini.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale aeternum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 13. augusti 1557.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem hoch- und wolgelerten, frommen und getruwen herren <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8009" cert="high">Johansen Schmiden</persName>, pfarreren zuͦ S. Martin ze <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>, sinem lieben herren und gevattern.</s>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
